snippet.title: NES Crackout (JP  Nazo no Kabe: Block-kuzushi)
snippet.description:
https://www.facebook.com/ShiryuVideoGames

"Hey you guys know "Breakout"? Taito has an awesome clone called "Arkanoid". I say we can do it too!" and that is how "Crackout was made, The End. Enjoy!
